188|The preceding sections define a constrained exceptional-geometric core. They do not by themselves define a UV-complete theory of flavor. The honest low-energy interpretation is an effective field theory in which spacetime fields describe slow deformations of the octonionic flavor vacuum, while a separate spurion sector supplies the observed CKM-localizing strain.
